problem with something,

00:11:53.870 --> 00:11:58.270 align:middle line:84%
or that we deny that
we are at war at all,

00:11:58.270 --> 00:12:01.460 align:middle line:84%
just by saying that
it's not there,

00:12:01.460 --> 00:12:03.400 align:middle line:84%
that we hope that
it's going to go away.

00:12:03.400 --> 00:12:06.950 align:middle line:84%
>> Denial is a large river
that runs through the--

00:12:06.950 --> 00:12:07.750 align:middle line:90%
no.

00:12:07.750 --> 00:12:09.050 align:middle line:90%
It's a joke-- denial.

00:12:09.050 --> 00:12:09.850 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:12:09.850 --> 00:12:11.610 align:middle line:90%
Denial.

00:12:11.610 --> 00:12:14.680 align:middle line:90%
>> I get it.

00:12:14.680 --> 00:12:17.800 align:middle line:84%
>> Denial is a huge
part of this problem.

00:12:17.800 --> 00:12:21.940 align:middle line:84%
