drives the circle of self.

00:12:21.940 --> 00:12:24.070 align:middle line:90%
And what is denial other than--

00:12:24.070 --> 00:12:25.930 align:middle line:90%
let's take a negative state.

00:12:25.930 --> 00:12:29.470 align:middle line:84%
Denial is on the
false part of myself,

00:12:29.470 --> 00:12:32.900 align:middle line:84%
this intimate
entity, the refusal

00:12:32.900 --> 00:12:36.370 align:middle line:90%
that says, oh, boy I better--

00:12:36.370 --> 00:12:41.660 align:middle line:84%
gee, if I go into that meeting
dressed in this outfit--

00:12:41.660 --> 00:12:43.580 align:middle line:90%
this is just a simple example--

00:12:43.580 --> 00:12:45.928 align:middle line:84%
everybody's going to
see that I'm an idiot.

00:12:45.928 --> 00:12:47.470 align:middle line:84%
And believe me, and
people maybe they

00:12:47.470 --> 00:12:49.150 align:middle line:84%
think that they
don't think that way.

00:12:49.150 --> 00:12:52.420 align:middle line:84%
We're always concerned
with the way we look.

00:12:52.420 --> 00:12:56.620 align:middle line:84%
Well, how many times have you
and I dressed to the nines,

00:12:56.620 --> 00:12:58.450 align:middle line:90%
to use an old expression.

00:12:58.450 --> 00:13:00.790 align:middle line:84%
And instead of being more
comfortable in a meeting,

00:13:00.790 --> 00:13:03.550 align:middle line:84%
found ourselves
more uncomfortable?

00:13:03.550 --> 00:13:06.610 align:middle line:84%
Well, denial is something
that operates in us when

00:13:06.610 --> 00:13:09.940 align:middle line:84%
we refuse to see that
that solution to that pain

00:13:09.940 --> 00:13:12.830 align:middle line:90%
doesn't provide any real relief.

00:13:12.830 --> 00:13:13.630 align:middle line:90%
So what do we do?

00:13:13.630 --> 00:13:15.220 align:middle line:84%
We just keep going
back through it.

00:13:15.220 --> 00:13:18.663 align:middle line:84%
But what's the machinery in
it is that the pain comes up,

00:13:18.663 --> 00:13:20.830 align:middle line:84%
and the fear comes up, and
it says, but you have to.

00:13:20.830 --> 00:13:22.060 align:middle line:90%
You've got to change that shirt.

00:13:22.060 --> 00:13:22.977 align:middle line:90%
You've got to do this.

00:13:22.977 --> 00:13:24.100 align:middle line:90%
You gotta do that.

00:13:24.100 --> 00:13:25.870 align:middle line:84%
And that pain drives
us around and around

00:13:25.870 --> 00:13:32.475 align:middle line:84%
and around, and we deny the
fact that that answer works.

00:13:32.475 --> 00:13:33.850 align:middle line:84%
If we could wake
up a little bit,

00:13:33.850 --> 00:13:36.443 align:middle line:84%
