00:16:54.450 --> 00:16:56.700 align:middle line:84%
to have that relationship
with life instead of the one

00:16:56.700 --> 00:16:59.160 align:middle line:84%
where I'm always trying
to prove myself in life.

00:16:59.160 --> 00:17:03.450 align:middle line:84%
I can start to taste
directly what these thoughts

00:17:03.450 --> 00:17:06.060 align:middle line:90%
and feelings are really doing.

00:17:06.060 --> 00:17:12.420 align:middle line:84%
