00:18:11.700 --> 00:18:14.380 align:middle line:84%
A whole new series of
thoughts just came to me.

00:18:14.380 --> 00:18:16.170 align:middle line:84%
Here we want have a
relationship with God.

00:18:16.170 --> 00:18:17.545 align:middle line:84%
Well, which one
of us is it going

00:18:17.545 --> 00:18:19.587 align:middle line:84%
