00:18:22.087 --> 00:18:23.530 align:middle line:90%
about money or sex or whatever?

00:18:23.530 --> 00:18:24.330 align:middle line:90%
See?

00:18:24.330 --> 00:18:28.020 align:middle line:84%
So all of these divided natures
waiting their opportunity

00:18:28.020 --> 00:18:30.600 align:middle line:84%
to get hold of my
