00:18:30.600 --> 00:18:33.340 align:middle line:84%
until certain circumstances
allow that relationship

00:18:33.340 --> 00:18:34.140 align:middle line:90%
to exist.

00:18:34.140 --> 00:18:36.180 align:middle line:84%
And then, all of a sudden,
I'm this kind of person.

00:18:36.180 --> 00:18:36.980 align:middle line:90%
I'm out at a party.

00:18:36.980 --> 00:18:38.920 align:middle line:90%
And I'm whatever it is.

00:18:38.920 --> 00:18:40.650 align:middle line:84%
And then the next
day, I am someone

00:18:40.650 --> 00:18:44.430 align:middle line:84%
who is beating himself up for
being such an exhibitionist.

00:18:44.430 --> 00:18:46.290 align:middle line:84%
Or I'm at a meeting,
and I'm taking charge.

00:18:46.290 --> 00:18:47.790 align:middle line:84%
And the next day, I don't
want to go to the meeting

00:18:47.790 --> 00:18:49.590 align:middle line:84%
because I don't know who I
am, and I'm afraid someone

00:18:49.590 --> 00:18:50.670 align:middle line:90%
will see I'm stupid.

00:18:50.670 --> 00:18:53.130 align:middle line:84%
All these rotating
personalities,

00:18:53.130 --> 00:18:56.460 align:middle line:84%
and every one of them
has my life for as long

00:18:56.460 --> 00:18:58.860 align:middle line:90%
as it's in charge of me.

00:18:58.860 --> 00:19:02.850 align:middle line:84%
The answer is not to
dominate one rotating self

00:19:02.850 --> 00:19:04.770 align:middle line:90%
with another rotating self.

00:19:04.770 --> 00:19:08.220 align:middle line:84%
It's to see the presence
of these multiple selves,

00:19:08.220 --> 00:19:12.210 align:middle line:84%
these energetic states,
