00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:17.490 align:middle line:84%
is lending a certain
energy to me that

00:19:17.490 --> 00:19:21.180 align:middle line:84%
produces a sense of myself
that I'm deriving my life from.

00:19:21.180 --> 00:19:24.330 align:middle line:84%
Then from that awareness,
a whole new eye,

00:19:24.330 --> 00:19:27.780 align:middle line:84%
a whole new self starts
to reveal itself.

00:19:27.780 --> 00:19:31.290 align:middle line:84%
And incidentally, this is what
that line is created with.

00:19:31.290 --> 00:19:33.090 align:middle line:84%
This is how God gets
in touch with us

00:19:33.090 --> 00:19:37.020 align:middle line:84%
is through that part of
