00:20:00.330 --> 00:20:01.560 align:middle line:90%
What do you think about that?

00:20:01.560 --> 00:20:05.470 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, it connects with
what I was saying earlier.

00:20:05.470 --> 00:20:08.010 align:middle line:84%
