00:20:10.380 --> 00:20:11.010 align:middle line:90%
You're good looking.

00:20:11.010 --> 00:20:11.670 align:middle line:90%
You're going to make it.

00:20:11.670 --> 00:20:12.470 align:middle line:90%
Everything's OK.

00:20:12.470 --> 00:20:13.350 align:middle line:90%
Everything is OK.

