00:20:33.480 --> 00:20:35.610 align:middle line:90%
But I don't catch that thought.

00:20:35.610 --> 00:20:38.230 align:middle line:84%
Instead, I catch that
thought's extension,

00:20:38.230 --> 00:20:41.160 align:middle line:84%
which says I better
affirm how good I am.

00:20:41.160 --> 00:20:44.340 align:middle line:84%
Well, if I affirm how
good I am, and it's

00:20:44.340 --> 00:20:47.910 align:middle line:84%
the secret opposite of the fear
that I'm not good enough, what

00:20:47.910 --> 00:20:49.950 align:middle line:84%
is really being
strengthened other

00:20:49.950 --> 00:20:54.570 align:middle line:84%
than this secret, sad,
self-defeating picture

00:20:54.570 --> 00:20:57.090 align:middle line:84%
I have of myself as
not being good enough?

