00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:11.640 align:middle line:84%
we can communicate and
extend our understanding

00:21:11.640 --> 00:21:14.440 align:middle line:84%
of the physical
universe that we're in.

00:21:14.440 --> 00:21:19.770 align:middle line:84%
But we are intended to be
human beings that are being.

00:21:19.770 --> 00:21:23.940 align:middle line:84%
What man taking thought can
